('83fcccb5-2e42-460a-89a7-7416667ea9df','Vs Fv1972;266',NULL,59.5987,16.7058,'henrikus','"Henricus',NULL,'Henricus.','1300-talet','latininskrift','Dörr','Furu','Västmanland','Sweden'),
('a19a685d-34f5-4b88-8de5-ba3390d389e7','Vs 14','L 1950',59.6508,16.8288,'guþ ⁓⁓ siɴe ⁓⁓ iþær ⁓⁓ mæstær ⁓⁓ ruþinger ⁓: ok ⁓ bo ⁓ fris ⁓⁓ o ⁓ alfa ⁓','"Guð signi iðar, mæistar "Rauðingʀ ok "Boi "Friss. O, Alfa','Gud signe er, mäster Röding och Bo fris. O, Alfa.','God may bless you, master Rauðingr and Búi Fríss. O, Alfa','Början av 1300-talet',NULL,'Dörrbeslag','Järn','Västmanland','Sweden'),
('28a009f3-5c1b-4ac0-87fc-5d244f596688','Vs 24','L 1006|L 1005',59.8731,16.3414,'buonti × kuþr × hulmkoetr × lit × resa × ufteʀ × oþintisu × kunu × seno × kumbr × hifrya × til × hasmuimura × iki betr × þon × byi raþr roþbalir × risti × runi × þisa × sikmuntaʀ × uaʀ … sestʀ × kuþ','Boandi goðr "Holmgautr let ræisa æftiʀ "Oðindisu, kunu sina. Kumbʀ hifrøya til "Hasumyra æigi bætri, þan byi raðr. "Rauð-Balliʀ risti runiʀ þessaʀ. "Sigmundaʀ vaʀ "[Oðindisa] systiʀ goð.',NULL,'The good husbandman Holmgautr had (the stone) raised in memory of Óðindísa, his wife. There will come to Hǫsumýrar no better housewife, who arranges the estate. Red-Balli carved these runes. Óðindísa was a good sister to Sigmundr.',NULL,NULL,'Runsten','Gnejs med vittrad yta','Västmanland','Sweden'),
