('4e9d2f0e-23ea-4847-b992-e69afe70f512','Vs 22','L 1004',59.7783,16.3796,'… + ytʀ : runfast · bruþur + s^in : hn : toþr : i : faru + runo : … (t)rka','… æftiʀ "Runfast, broður sinn. Hann [varð] dauðr i faru "Runa … drængia.',NULL,'… in memory of Rúnfastr, his brother. He died on a voyage. Runa … / He died on Runi''s voyage … of valiant men.',NULL,NULL,'Runsten','Granit','Västmanland','Sweden'),
('390b325d-416e-4d5d-a94f-3b91f13d9ad9','Vs 32',NULL,59.9478,16.2747,'… -- × si--on × sik × au(k) × -… …-no × auk × (f)aþu- …','… [at] si[alf]an sik ok … [þe]nna ok faðu[r] …',NULL,'… in memory of himself and … this … and father …',NULL,'Ev. är Vs 33 en del av denna sten.','Fragment av runsten','Rödgrå granit','Västmanland','Sweden'),
('82261d6c-a62c-4249-93ad-db83bc5a34f6','Vs 23','L 1007',59.8912,16.3757,'[…ui… × lit × ri-… …iþun × e(f)ti × …l… …lir × …b… …----num × --þi × re---niraeft(ʀ)-…]','"… lét … … eptir … … … … … …','… lät … efter(?) …','… had … in memory of …',NULL,NULL,'Runsten','Mörkgrå glimmerskiffer','Västmanland','Sweden'),
('03c333d9-5e56-4adf-83f7-ab2f98181006','Vs 17','L 1001|B 1085|L 1000',59.6808,16.7693,'holmste[n] : let : resa : mer[ki : eftir : tifrit : gonu : sina : ok : iftir] : sik : sel¶fan :','"Holmsteinn lét reisa merki eptir "Tíðfríð, konu sína, ok eptir sik sjalfan.','Holmsten lät resa minnesmärket efter Tidfrid, sin hustru, och efter sig själv.','Holmsteinn had the landmark raised in memory of Tíðfríðr, his wife, and in memory of himself.',NULL,'Bild av skepp.','Runsten','Granit','Västmanland','Sweden'),
('e3bb20ee-73d3-40ef-bebd-a5e539522e48','Vs 9','L 1016|B 1082',59.5899,16.4936,'× kisl × lit × kera × buru × eftʀ × osl × sun × sin × han u(a)[rþ] × tyþr × a eklati × kuþ ialbi × has × ont auk × selu','"Gísl lét gera brú eptir "Ásl/"Ǫsl, son sinn. Hann varð dauðr á "Englandi. "Guð hjalpi hans ǫnd ok sálu.',NULL,'Gísl had the bridge made in memory of Ásl/Ǫsl, his son. He died in England. May God help his spirit and soul.',NULL,'Parsten till Vs 10.','Runsten','Granit','Västmanland','Sweden'),
